dct_description_sm: Shows settlements, roads, and anchorages. Depths shown by soundings. Facsimile. In lower margin: From the collection of charts and plans made by order of the Duke de Choiseul and executed by S. Bellin in 1764. In lower margin: Lith for D.T. Valentine's Manual, for 1861.
